      CompletableFuture<CardinalityResponse> issueCardinalityRequest(SPARQLRequest req, SPARQLEndpoint fm) throws FederationAccessException
      Requests the cardinality of the result of the given request. Assumes that the given request contains a SPARQLGraphPattern rather than a full SPARQLQuery. If it does not, then this method throws an IllegalArgumentException.
